<h1>Reservation Reminder</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @first_name %> <%= @last_name %>,</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming reservation.</p>
<% if @downpayment.present? && @downpayment > 0 %>
  <p>
    We received your downpayment of <%= number_to_currency(@downpayment, unit: "PHP") %>.
    The remaining balance of <%= number_to_currency(@total - @downpayment, unit: "PHP") %> 
    is due on the day of the reservation.
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
    Thank you for your reservation. Below are your Reservation Details.
  </p>
<% end %>
<h2>Reservation Details</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Reservation Date:</strong> <%= @reservation_date %></li>
  <li><strong>Meal Period:</strong> <%= @meal_period %> 
  <% if @meal_period.to_s.downcase == "lunch" %>(11:00 AM) 
  <% else %> 
  (6:00 PM) 
  <% end %></li>
  <li><strong>Number of Guests:</strong> <%= @number_of_guest %></li>
  <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @email %></li>
  <li><strong>Mobile Number:</strong> <%= @mobile_number %></li>
</ul>
<strong> Reminder: Please be at the venue 30 minutes before <%= @meal_period %> time </strong>  
<p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your reservation, please contact us.</p>

<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>Your Restaurant Team</p>